# Jurisdictions

When the National Zoning Atlas began, no one knew how many jurisdictions could exercise zoning in the U.S because there was no centralized national database. So we built one.

Our team stewards the first and only fully integrated dataset that has identified all 33,000+ jurisdictions with zoning authority in the country — complete with their geographic boundaries, population and housing unit counts, and land cover statistics.

